	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So the PlayChoice is the only &quot;NES&quot; machine that uses RGB I assume? I tried looking for these values but got lost in the massive amount of topics trying to emulate the NTSC video.<br /><br />Are Nestopia's RGB values taken from the PC10? If not, where can I find them? Your help is appreciated. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_mrgreen.gif" alt=":mrgreen:" title="Mr. Green" /> This is for an NES-style PC game I'm working on. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_mrgreen.gif" alt=":mrgreen:" title="Mr. Green" />

		

		</td>
